                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8de3e4c9-abb3-4e30-97bc-e3c41757254b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
